OL,3,CDelayed post causing 'nightmare' for
OL,4,Cfrustrated Cornish town
OL,6,FPeople in West Cornwall say problems
OL,7,Fwith post being delayed or lost is
OL,8,Fturning into a 'nightmare'.
OL,10,FSome residents told ITV News they have
OL,11,Fmissed vital medical appointments due
OL,12,Fto letters not arriving in time.
OL,14,FZoe Simmons, who runs an accountancy
OL,15,Ffirm on the outskirts of Helston, says
OL,16,Fdelayed or lost post can have serious
OL,17,Fconsequences for her customers.
