OL,3,CDelayed post causing 'nightmare' for
OL,4,Cfrustrated Cornish town
OL,6,F"We deal with a lot of letters from
OL,7,FHMRC and from clients, and at the
OL,8,Fmoment we're lucky to get one postal
OL,9,Fdelivery a week," Zoe said.
OL,11,F"We're actually having to have staff
OL,12,Fgo down and pick up the post from the
OL,13,Fsorting office, but they're only open
OL,14,Ffrom 8am to 10am.
OL,16,F"We normally expect to be getting
OL,17,Faround 20 and 30 letters a day and
OL,18,Feight days is our longest time span
OL,19,Fwithout having received any post at
OL,20,Fall."
