OL,3,CDelayed post causing 'nightmare' for
OL,4,Cfrustrated Cornish town
OL,6,FRoyal Mail says the disruption is
OL,7,Ftemporary and they are working hard to
OL,8,Fget things back to normal. But Liberal
OL,9,FDemocrat MP Andrew George told us the
OL,10,Fsituation is becoming untenable.
OL,12,FService under 'incredible stress'
OL,14,FBut Liberal Democrat MP Andrew George
OL,15,Fsaid the situation is becoming
OL,16,Funtenable.J"Delivery services are
OL,17,Funder a lot of pressure, but Royal
OL,18,FMail in particular," Mr George said.
