OL,4,Cfrustrated Cornish town
OL,6,FA Royal Mail spokesman said: "We are
OL,7,Fexperiencing temporary disruption to
OL,8,Fdeliveries in the area due to higher
OL,9,Fparcel volumes and short-term
OL,10,Fresourcing pressures.
OL,12,F"Additional support is being provided
OL,13,Fto the local operation, and we are
OL,14,Fworking hard to restore normal
OL,15,Fdeliveries as quickly as possible."
